		<h1 class="page_title">Japan&#8217;s Debt Problem Visualized</h1>

						
		<div class="post-content">
			<p class="meta-info" id="meta-info-blog">Posted  by <a href="http://www.addogram.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by Aftab Singh" rel="author">Aftab Singh</a></p>			<p>Here we present a short visual explanation of Japan&#8217;s debt problem. In just a few short minutes you&#8217;ll have a deep understanding of Japan&#8217;s (impending) debt crisis.</p>
<p><span id="more-2618"></span></p>
