				<p>Very nicely done &#8212; The only thing I wld add is that the Central Bank is also clearly targeting a massive depreciation of the Japanese Yen, which in theory will again lead to a large trade surplus through higher exports .  The only problem with that is every country is trying to do the same thing with their currency, there is a currency war in play .</p>
				
				<div class="reply-container"><a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/04/japans-debt-crisis-visualized/?replytocom=195#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-195", "195", "respond", "2618")'>Reply</a></div>			</div> <!-- end comment-content-->
